---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import ImageText from '../components/ImageText.astro';
import BookingCTA from '../components/BookingCTA.astro';
---
<Layout
	title="Our Clinic"
	description="Explore Balance Performance Physiotherapy, 9 treatment rooms, two studios, reception shop and ergonomic showroom in Clapham, London."
>
	<PageHero
		title="Clinic"
		highlight="Our"
		subtitle="9 treatment rooms, a reception shop, and two full movement studios, everything you need under one roof."
		breadcrumb="Our Clinic"
	/>

	<ImageText
		eyebrow="Reception"
		heading="A warm welcome at"
		highlight="reception"
		image="/our-clinic/reception.jpg"
		imageAlt="Balance Performance Physiotherapy reception area"
	>
		<p>We have a large comfortable reception and waiting area for you if you don't want to go into the gym or studio to move and warm yourself before your session.</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Bike rack and buggy space</li>
			<li>Wheelchair ramp at front door (buzzer controlled)</li>
			<li>Dynamic reception chairs and a standing desk for emails</li>
			<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
			<li>Healthy snacks, coconut water, organic juices</li>
			<li>A shop stocked for protection, performance, recovery and rehab</li>
		</ul>
	</ImageText>

	<ImageText
		eyebrow="Treatment rooms"
		heading="9 rooms,"
		highlight="purpose-built"
		reverse
		altBg
		image="/our-clinic/treatment-rooms.jpg"
		imageAlt="Balance Physio treatment room"
	>
		<p>We have 9 treatment rooms, 4 downstairs and 5 on the first floor. Our massage services take place in the Early Rehab Studio quiet rooms and a dedicated medical room is available for ultrasound examinations.</p>
		<p>All rooms have adequate heating and ventilation, with clean towels and frequently changed bed and pillow covers.</p>
		<p>Our philosophy is not to spend too much time in treatment rooms, the real work happens in the studios and gym.</p>
	</ImageText>

	<ImageText
		eyebrow="Home working"
		heading="Painful, tight and tense"
		highlight="at home?"
		image="/our-clinic/home-working.jpg"
		imageAlt="Laptop on a home working desk"
	>
		<p>Since the era of COVID-19, working from home has increased massively and we have seen the consequences at Balance.</p>
		<p>Our physiotherapists, osteopaths, soft tissue therapists and movement and breathwork coaches offer workplace assessments at Balance, at your office, or in your home. A video analysis service is also available with recommendations supplied on memory stick for HR or a workplace assessor to review.</p>
	</ImageText>

	<ImageText
		eyebrow="WorkSpace"
		heading="A showroom for"
		highlight="smarter work"
		reverse
		altBg
		image="/our-clinic/workspace.jpg"
		imageAlt="Keyboard and ergonomic desk setup"
	>
		<p>We have sourced a wealth of products that will refine every difficult working situation, seating and desk solutions, keyboards, mice, laptop stands, monitor arms and bespoke office furniture. Come and try before you buy.</p>
	</ImageText>

	<BookingCTA />
</Layout>
